{"lastModified":1775138994873,"uri":"c::10120242293::vessel::d5cca3bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nStep aboard the luxurious Lagoon 620 “Adriatic Lion,” a sophisticated 62-ft (18.90m) catamaran designed for the discerning traveler. With its expansive 5 double guest cabins, each equipped with en-suite bathrooms, “Adriatic Lion” offers an indulgent retreat for up to 10 guests. This luxury vessel is crewed by a team of three professionals, including a Captain, Chef, and Stewardess, ensuring a seamless and unforgettable charter experience. \n\nWhether you're relaxing on the spacious flybridge with its sunbathing area, enjoying gourmet meals prepared by your private chef, or exploring the waters with a range of exciting water toys, “Adriatic Lion” is the perfect blend of comfort, style, and adventure. \n\nThe name \"Adriatic Lion\" blends the majestic power of a lion with the beauty of the Adriatic Sea. Adriatic evokes the stunning waters and rich heritage of the region, while Lion symbolizes strength, courage, and regality. Together, they reflect a yacht that offers luxury, adventure, and a commanding presence on the water. ","blueprint":{"name":"ADRIATIC LION","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fb433990-fdcb-11ef-9b6c-1fb08ee7fa87/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fb43d5d0-fdcb-11ef-9b6d-1fb08ee7fa87/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fb418be0-fdcb-11ef-9b6b-1fb08ee7fa87/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fb4116b0-fdcb-11ef-9b6b-1fb08ee7fa87/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::fb45aa90-fdcb-11ef-9b6e-1fb08ee7fa87/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::asset